Field Detail

keepHighlights

public boolean keepHighlights
Keep query word highlighting. Yahoo by default highlights query words in snippets using the bold HTML tag. Set this attribute to true to keep these highlights.

Attribute label:
Keep highlights
Attribute level:
Advanced
Attribute group:

service

public YahooSearchService service
The specific search service to be used by this document source. You can use this attribute to choose which Yahoo! service to query, e.g. Yahoo Web Search or Yahoo News.
